Package: libimage-base-gtk2-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: libimage-base-perl (>= 1.12), libgtk2-perl, ${perl:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Draw into Gtk2 windows, pixmaps, pixbuf and images.
 An Image::Base extension to operate on Gtk2 windows
 (Gtk2::Gdk::Window), pixmaps (Gtk2::Gdk::Pixmap), pixbufs
 (Gtk2::Gdk::Pixbuf) and images (Gtk2::Gdk::Image).
